title: Mega Batting Cages
description:
Our most popular attraction! 
Up to three mega-sized batting cages complete with a powerful pitching system!
otherRequirements: Includes bats, softballs and cage safety chain

title: Fireballin'
description: A spin on the classic arcade game, but with full-size backetballs! Our exclusive custom-built basketball arcade can challenge 4 players at once.

title: Top Shot Hockey
description:
Showcase your hockey skills! Our Electronic Hockey Net is a full-size hockey net that offers five separate player challenges. Participants shoot pucks at the electronic net with the goal to shoot quickly, accurately and decisively at lit targets. Our most popular game Face-Off
Target practice! Take your best shot. All nine targets light up, but how fast can you knock out each? Timer records to the nearest 1/100th of a second.

title: Hang Time
description: Showcase your iron grip! Hold on to our motorized rig to take the ultimate test of muscular endurance.

title: Quarterback Challenge
description: Can you get rid of your footballs before your oppennt?  Simple and fun. each player strats the game with 3 footballs. when your ball goes through the hole now your oppennt must get rid of it. first player to be left with no balls on his side wins!

title: Football Showdown
description: Hone your passing skills with a game that pits your passing skills against a detemined human goalie. Every successful pass releases a burst from our attached smoke machine!
otherRequirements: Needs good ventilation if smoke machine is used indoors

title: Vertical Jump
description: Reach for the sky! Break through the high-jump record with our intunitive jump challenge.

title: 40 Yard Dash
description: Race along our custom 40-yard runners in this classic test of fitness. Our precision laser timing system captures every millisecond of your performance!

title: Over the Endzone
description: Catch our machine-launched footballs as you jump unto our enourmous bouncy pad!

title: 3-point Shootout Racks
description: Turn any backetball court into a professional tournament with our racks and real-time LED scoreboard!

title: 3-point Shootout Dr Dish
description: Turn any backetball court into a professional tournament with our racks and real-time LED scoreboard!

title: Radar Gun Inflatable
description: Unleash your fasted pitch at our inflatable target. Our specialized radar gun can put a number on your incredble speed!

title: Homerun Derby
description: Take batting practice to a whole new level with our pro-grade pitching system and vast supply of balls!

title: Smart Scoreboard
description: Our in-house, custom built smart scorebaord keeps track of all game scores so everyone can join in the fun! Can you make it into our all-time Hall of Fame?
